summary: An ordinance relating to the improvement of Northeast 90th Street from 17th Ave. Northeast to Bothell Way Northeast; and certain other streets and avenues, by constructing watermains, together with fire hydrants and otherwise improving the same; as authorized by Ordinance No. 91106, creating Local Improvement District No. 6263; eliminating certain streets and avenues from said local improvement district and amending Section 1 of said ordinance.
